<h2 class="bold font-l">"Apologize to your sister!"</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Rikka improperly spends the money Touka gives to her, and Yuuta punishes her when he finds out. </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ComedicSpanking" class='trope-example-link'>Comedic Spanking</a></p>
</div>
